mail.module
INSTALL

Requirements
------------

Sending of attachments requires the upload module to be enabled
and uploads configured for mail nodes, or other content types
for which mailing is enabled.

Installation
------------

Create a new "mail" directory in your "modules" directory and copy
the two files mail.module and activeMailLib.php to the new directory.

Go to "modules" under "site configuration" in the administration 
pages and enable the module.




